1
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:13,000
"Double Helix"

2
00:01:16,080 --> 00:01:17,680
Let me consult the stars.

3
00:01:17,960 --> 00:01:20,720
Your love life is destined
to be a rocky road.

4
00:01:21,200 --> 00:01:24,600
You'll be entangled with
men for the rest of your life.

5
00:01:24,760 --> 00:01:25,760
And furthermore,

6
00:01:28,960 --> 00:01:30,120
you haven't even paid me yet.

7
00:01:30,400 --> 00:01:32,336
You couldn't even tell if
it was a man or a woman,

8
00:01:32,360 --> 00:01:33,240
and you still want to get paid?

9
00:01:33,360 --> 00:01:34,496
The only reason I didn't flip your stall

10
00:01:34,520 --> 00:01:36,120
is because I'm feeling charitable today.

11
00:02:14,400 --> 00:02:15,400
Good morning, Mr. Lu.

12
00:02:26,000 --> 00:02:27,720
Who put this money tree here?

13
00:02:28,600 --> 00:02:30,000
Everyone, listen up!

14
00:02:30,480 --> 00:02:31,800
The manager wants everyone

15
00:02:31,880 --> 00:02:34,400
to change their desktop screens to

16
00:02:34,480 --> 00:02:36,280
the most polished presentation models.

17
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:37,400
Hurry, hurry!

18
00:02:37,400 --> 00:02:38,400
Get moving, get moving!

19
00:02:42,960 --> 00:02:43,960
Still eating?

20
00:02:44,120 --> 00:02:45,280
Clean up your desk right now!

21
00:02:48,800 --> 00:02:49,880
Mr. Lu, Mr. Lu!

22
00:02:50,880 --> 00:02:51,880
Mr. Lu.

23
00:03:02,110 --> 00:03:03,783
[Tabloid headline about the engagement
betwen Lu Feng and a real estate heiress]

24
00:03:05,313 --> 00:03:06,313
What's going on?

25
00:03:08,040 --> 00:03:09,240
The new boss arrived early.

26
00:03:10,280 --> 00:03:11,360
What new boss?

27
00:03:12,040 --> 00:03:13,880
The one they announced
in last week's meeting.

28
00:03:13,906 --> 00:03:15,266
Right, you weren't here last week.

29
00:03:16,280 --> 00:03:17,560
It's our chairman's

30
00:03:17,606 --> 00:03:19,046
legendary only son.

31
00:03:19,280 --> 00:03:20,496
I heard he just got back from the States.

32
00:03:20,520 --> 00:03:22,000
From the States?

33
00:03:23,013 --> 00:03:24,093
America.

34
00:03:24,680 --> 00:03:26,400
He's here, he's here! The new boss is here!

35
00:03:44,240 --> 00:03:45,520
Good morning, Mr. Lu.

36
00:03:50,240 --> 00:03:50,800
Mr. Lu.

37
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:53,080
These are our colleagues
from the design department.

38
00:04:00,753 --> 00:04:01,753
Cheng Yichen.

39
00:04:04,733 --> 00:04:05,733
Long time no see.

40
00:04:11,040 --> 00:04:12,040
Lu Feng.

41
00:04:13,480 --> 00:04:15,000
Can you promise me something?

42
00:04:17,040 --> 00:04:19,400
If we ever break up one day,

43
00:04:20,480 --> 00:04:21,480
the ring...

44
00:04:22,400 --> 00:04:23,480
don't ask for it back.

45
00:04:24,680 --> 00:04:26,000
I can pay you for it.

46
00:04:27,080 --> 00:04:28,080
Just let me keep it.

47
00:04:28,400 --> 00:04:29,400
Okay?

48
00:04:29,920 --> 00:04:31,400
We're never going to break up.

49
00:04:33,720 --> 00:04:35,400
I want to be with you forever.

50
00:04:39,040 --> 00:04:41,240
Yichen, you know Mr. Lu?

51
00:04:42,720 --> 00:04:44,160
We were high school classmates.

52
00:04:44,800 --> 00:04:45,800
Back then,

53
00:04:46,320 --> 00:04:47,760
I guess we were pretty good friends.

54
00:04:48,560 --> 00:04:49,600
We weren't really friends.

55
00:04:50,706 --> 00:04:52,546
I wouldn't dare presume
to be close to Mr. Lu.

56
00:04:58,246 --> 00:04:58,886
Mr. Lu,

57
00:04:59,220 --> 00:05:00,980
shall we head over to
the other departments?

58
00:05:05,079 --> 00:05:06,439
Carry on with your work, everyone.

59
00:05:10,800 --> 00:05:13,200
Cheng Yichen, you're
about to hit the jackpot!

60
00:05:13,520 --> 00:05:14,880
You're classmates with the boss?

61
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:16,920
You should really make an effort.

62
00:05:17,333 --> 00:05:19,013
Catch up and build a rapport.

63
00:05:19,880 --> 00:05:21,200
We haven't spoken in years.

64
00:05:21,520 --> 00:05:22,936
We weren't that close to begin with.

65
00:05:22,960 --> 00:05:24,200
There's nothing to catch up on.

66
00:05:55,207 --> 00:05:56,447
It really has been a long time.

67
00:05:59,473 --> 00:06:00,473
Xiao Chen.

68
00:06:01,466 --> 00:06:02,506
Long time no see.

69
00:06:09,959 --> 00:06:11,399
Why aren't you wearing your glasses?

70
00:06:19,200 --> 00:06:20,200
Xiao Chen.

71
00:06:20,800 --> 00:06:22,400
I've been in the States all these years.

72
00:06:23,080 --> 00:06:24,400
Actually, for a while,

73
00:06:25,906 --> 00:06:27,186
I did forget about you.

74
00:06:33,980 --> 00:06:34,980
Yeah.

75
00:06:35,340 --> 00:06:36,340
That's normal.

76
00:06:36,500 --> 00:06:37,980
It's been over four years, after all.

77
00:06:39,600 --> 00:06:40,600
All these years,

78
00:06:41,000 --> 00:06:42,640
I thought I'd never be able to come back,

79
00:06:46,240 --> 00:06:47,560
or see you ever again.

80
00:06:49,640 --> 00:06:50,640
So...

81
00:06:50,680 --> 00:06:51,680
I understand.

82
00:06:52,960 --> 00:06:53,960
I understand it all.

83
00:06:56,080 --> 00:06:58,160
Actually, I've been the
same as you all these years.

84
00:06:58,360 --> 00:06:59,560
Busy with my studies,

85
00:06:59,680 --> 00:07:00,760
and lots of family matters.

86
00:07:01,440 --> 00:07:02,520
Actually, some things,

87
00:07:03,920 --> 00:07:05,160
I don't really remember either.

88
00:07:05,320 --> 00:07:06,320
But I...

89
00:07:11,360 --> 00:07:12,360
Oh, right.

90
00:07:12,680 --> 00:07:14,480
I saw the news report a while back.

91
00:07:14,760 --> 00:07:16,120
Your fiancée is beautiful.

92
00:07:18,800 --> 00:07:19,880
Before long,

93
00:07:20,360 --> 00:07:21,976
you'll probably be getting married, right?

94
00:07:22,000 --> 00:07:23,000
When that happens,

95
00:07:23,520 --> 00:07:24,920
make sure to send me an invitation.

96
00:07:25,680 --> 00:07:26,880
After all,

97
00:07:27,320 --> 00:07:28,600
we are friends, aren't we?

98
00:07:29,000 --> 00:07:30,000
Of course.

99
00:07:30,200 --> 00:07:31,200
When I get married,

100
00:07:32,120 --> 00:07:33,280
I'll definitely send you one too.

101
00:07:33,440 --> 00:07:34,440
When the time comes,

102
00:07:34,600 --> 00:07:36,120
you must do me the honor of attending.

103
00:07:36,520 --> 00:07:37,720
You have a girlfriend?

104
00:07:39,200 --> 00:07:40,200
Yeah, yeah.

105
00:07:42,840 --> 00:07:44,080
Is it the one with long hair,

106
00:07:44,160 --> 00:07:45,240
sitting next to you?

107
00:07:47,600 --> 00:07:48,480
She must be getting impatient.

108
00:07:48,600 --> 00:07:49,600
I'll get going now.

109
00:08:00,560 --> 00:08:01,560
Hello.

110
00:08:02,920 --> 00:08:03,960
Cheng Yichen.

111
00:08:04,480 --> 00:08:05,480
What a coincidence.

112
00:08:07,040 --> 00:08:08,040
Lu Feng.

113
00:08:08,680 --> 00:08:10,960
Do you want to be on the bottom,

114
00:08:11,640 --> 00:08:12,680
or on top?

115
00:08:16,680 --> 00:08:17,680
On top.

116
00:08:19,280 --> 00:08:19,920
I'm Wang Nan.

117
00:08:20,040 --> 00:08:20,640
I'm Shang Kun.

118
00:08:20,720 --> 00:08:22,120
Are you our last roommate?

119
00:08:22,720 --> 00:08:23,400
Cheng Yichen.

120
00:08:23,600 --> 00:08:24,840
We were high school classmates.

121
00:08:25,440 --> 00:08:26,440
What a coincidence.

122
00:08:26,760 --> 00:08:28,336
Don't just stand in the
doorway, come on in.

123
00:08:28,360 --> 00:08:29,360
Okay.

124
00:08:31,240 --> 00:08:32,600
This is too much of a coincidence.

125
00:08:35,160 --> 00:08:36,160
Let me show you the dorm.

126
00:08:37,040 --> 00:08:38,040
Let's go.

127
00:08:39,300 --> 00:08:41,800
(Episode 1: Cheng Yichen, long time no see)

128
00:09:06,760 --> 00:09:07,920
Go, go, go, Cheng Yichen!

129
00:09:08,040 --> 00:09:09,040
- Go! - Go where?

130
00:09:09,400 --> 00:09:10,479
Run, Cheng Yichen!

131
00:09:10,480 --> 00:09:11,480
Run where?

132
00:09:11,720 --> 00:09:13,039
You're about to get
caught! Run back, run back!

133
00:09:13,040 --> 00:09:14,040
Back where?

134
00:09:14,120 --> 00:09:14,680
Come on!

135
00:09:15,120 --> 00:09:16,120
Wait, wait, wait!

136
00:09:16,160 --> 00:09:17,840
There's a chance, there's a chance! I'm...

137
00:09:18,120 --> 00:09:19,120
Yes, yes, yes! Yes!

138
00:09:19,400 --> 00:09:20,440
That was awesome!

139
00:09:22,840 --> 00:09:24,400
Look at that move!

140
00:09:27,880 --> 00:09:28,640
Alright, students.

141
00:09:28,800 --> 00:09:30,680
Today we'll cover basic economic functions.

142
00:09:31,520 --> 00:09:33,560
Economic functions mainly include

143
00:09:33,840 --> 00:09:34,840
demand functions,

144
00:09:35,600 --> 00:09:36,640
supply functions,

145
00:09:37,040 --> 00:09:38,040
cost functions,

146
00:09:38,720 --> 00:09:40,200
then revenue functions,

147
00:09:40,880 --> 00:09:41,880
and profit functions.

148
00:09:42,800 --> 00:09:44,400
You can take some quick notes.

149
00:09:47,920 --> 00:09:49,760
You want me to tutor you?

150
00:09:51,280 --> 00:09:51,840
Please!

151
00:09:51,840 --> 00:09:52,800
But my grades

152
00:09:52,801 --> 00:09:55,160
aren't good enough to tutor you.

153
00:09:55,480 --> 00:09:57,000
You're more than qualified to help me.

154
00:09:57,160 --> 00:09:58,576
I don't understand anything in class.

155
00:09:58,600 --> 00:10:01,200
No matter how many times the
teacher explains it, I don't get it.

156
00:10:09,280 --> 00:10:15,520
Pi plus h plus x equals p plus n plus...

157
00:10:29,960 --> 00:10:32,080
equals p plus t.

158
00:10:34,920 --> 00:10:36,280
I don't understand this part here.

159
00:10:36,600 --> 00:10:37,600
Because...

160
00:10:38,360 --> 00:10:40,280
y is negative.

161
00:10:56,840 --> 00:10:57,840
Xiao Chen.

162
00:10:57,880 --> 00:10:58,960
Thanks for tutoring me.

163
00:10:59,320 --> 00:11:00,600
Let me take you out to eat now.

164
00:11:01,280 --> 00:11:02,760
The grades aren't even out yet.

165
00:11:03,200 --> 00:11:04,400
I owe you one anyway.

166
00:11:15,840 --> 00:11:16,840
If...

167
00:11:17,080 --> 00:11:19,280
if you have time, I'd really
like to go roller skating.

168
00:11:21,640 --> 00:11:23,080
Why are you looking at me like that?

169
00:11:24,080 --> 00:11:25,480
Has anyone ever told you

170
00:11:25,960 --> 00:11:27,680
that those glasses are ugly?

171
00:11:27,880 --> 00:11:28,600
You look like a mushroom.

172
00:11:28,680 --> 00:11:30,840
I wear them because my eyes are ugly.

173
00:11:32,080 --> 00:11:32,680
I don't believe you.

174
00:11:32,840 --> 00:11:33,480
Let me see.

175
00:11:33,680 --> 00:11:34,120
No.

176
00:11:34,200 --> 00:11:35,000
What if I scare you?

177
00:11:35,120 --> 00:11:36,120
Yeah, Xiao Chen.

178
00:11:36,160 --> 00:11:37,880
We've never seen you without your glasses.

179
00:11:38,040 --> 00:11:39,200
Take them off and let us see.

180
00:11:55,000 --> 00:11:55,680
Xiao Chen.

181
00:11:56,000 --> 00:11:57,400
Actually, you look

182
00:11:57,520 --> 00:11:58,840
pretty cute without your glasses.

183
00:12:02,280 --> 00:12:03,400
You'd better put them back on.

184
00:12:03,440 --> 00:12:04,440
I know.

185
00:12:04,800 --> 00:12:06,720
I'm not cruel enough to
go out and scare people.

186
00:12:10,800 --> 00:12:13,880
Don't ever take your glasses
off in front of anyone else again.

187
00:12:14,040 --> 00:12:15,080
I know.

188
00:12:18,320 --> 00:12:19,320
You know what I mean.

189
00:12:20,560 --> 00:12:22,000
If you think my eyes are ugly,

190
00:12:22,200 --> 00:12:23,480
then stay away from me.

191
00:12:27,000 --> 00:12:28,080
What I mean is,

192
00:12:29,040 --> 00:12:31,480
you look really good without your glasses.

193
00:12:32,040 --> 00:12:33,040
Even I

194
00:12:33,800 --> 00:12:34,800
want to kiss you.

195
00:12:35,800 --> 00:12:36,920
I'm a grown man!

196
00:12:37,040 --> 00:12:38,360
Are you crazy?

197
00:12:44,160 --> 00:12:45,160
Xiao Chen,

198
00:12:46,240 --> 00:12:47,320
you washed my socks?

199
00:12:48,080 --> 00:12:49,680
Those socks were practically fossilized.

200
00:12:49,880 --> 00:12:52,080
Why are you so good to me?

201
00:12:55,160 --> 00:12:56,360
You're a pervert!

202
00:12:58,913 --> 00:12:59,913
I'm a pervert?

203
00:13:00,200 --> 00:13:00,960
If I'm a pervert,

204
00:13:01,080 --> 00:13:02,080
then I'll kiss here too.

205
00:13:02,640 --> 00:13:03,880
Are you out of your mind?

206
00:13:08,000 --> 00:13:09,760
- Cheng Yichen, you're ticklish?
- That tickles!

207
00:13:09,960 --> 00:13:11,400
You're going to tickle me to death!

208
00:13:12,960 --> 00:13:14,120
Why are you so "sensitive"?

209
00:13:18,240 --> 00:13:19,240
Why are you...

210
00:13:20,040 --> 00:13:22,120
It's just being ticklish.
Why use such a weird word?

211
00:13:25,200 --> 00:13:26,200
Why are you...

212
00:13:27,040 --> 00:13:28,160
acting so strange?

213
00:13:28,880 --> 00:13:30,880
Did you bump your head earlier?

214
00:13:33,120 --> 00:13:34,120
Tomorrow,

215
00:13:35,040 --> 00:13:36,280
let's go roller skating.

216
00:13:43,400 --> 00:13:44,560
You know how to roller skate?

217
00:13:46,280 --> 00:13:47,680
Is there anything I can't do?

218
00:14:38,880 --> 00:14:40,680
Lu Feng, maybe we should do something else.

219
00:14:41,680 --> 00:14:42,680
Don't be afraid.

220
00:14:42,920 --> 00:14:43,960
You won't die from a fall.

221
00:14:44,120 --> 00:14:45,520
You're going to be the death of me.

222
00:14:46,200 --> 00:14:47,600
I'm here, don't worry.

223
00:14:47,880 --> 00:14:49,016
I promise you won't get hurt.

224
00:14:49,040 --> 00:14:50,160
I have confidence in myself.

225
00:14:50,440 --> 00:14:51,440
Come on.

226
00:15:09,280 --> 00:15:10,360
Make way, make way!

227
00:15:12,520 --> 00:15:13,760
Are you blind or what?

228
00:15:18,440 --> 00:15:19,520
Does it hurt here too?

229
00:15:20,240 --> 00:15:21,240
How about...

230
00:15:21,560 --> 00:15:22,240
I'll rub it for you?

231
00:15:22,240 --> 00:15:23,000
No, no, no.

232
00:15:23,200 --> 00:15:24,200
No need.

233
00:15:24,840 --> 00:15:25,840
It doesn't really hurt.

234
00:15:28,800 --> 00:15:30,096
Yichen, what happened to your foot?

235
00:15:30,120 --> 00:15:31,120
Don't ask.

236
00:15:31,360 --> 00:15:32,360
I twisted it by accident.

237
00:15:33,880 --> 00:15:35,200
But class is starting soon.

238
00:15:35,640 --> 00:15:37,280
The professor is teaching data analysis.

239
00:15:37,480 --> 00:15:39,336
And I don't know what's
gotten into him lately.

240
00:15:39,360 --> 00:15:40,439
He's obsessed with printing out

241
00:15:40,440 --> 00:15:41,080
everyone's name

242
00:15:41,160 --> 00:15:42,280
and doing the roll call one by one.

243
00:15:43,320 --> 00:15:44,320
Anyway,

244
00:15:44,640 --> 00:15:45,896
can you even go to class like this?

245
00:15:45,920 --> 00:15:47,376
Should I ask for a leave
of absence for you?

246
00:15:47,400 --> 00:15:49,280
No, I have to go.

247
00:15:51,200 --> 00:15:52,440
How are you going to manage?

248
00:15:53,200 --> 00:15:55,440
How about you say something nice,

249
00:15:56,000 --> 00:15:57,000
and I'll help you out?

250
00:15:57,560 --> 00:15:58,656
The professor knows who's who.

251
00:15:58,680 --> 00:15:59,720
How are you going to help?

252
00:16:04,240 --> 00:16:05,240
Like this.

253
00:16:26,280 --> 00:16:27,240
Who told you to walk on your own?

254
00:16:27,240 --> 00:16:28,240
Never mind that.

255
00:16:29,760 --> 00:16:30,760
My shoe!

256
00:16:30,920 --> 00:16:32,280
My shoe!

257
00:16:33,160 --> 00:16:34,360
My shoe!

258
00:16:35,160 --> 00:16:36,440
Shoe!

259
00:16:37,000 --> 00:16:38,080
Lu Feng!

260
00:16:38,520 --> 00:16:40,440
Do you think I'm a sack of potatoes?

261
00:16:40,560 --> 00:16:41,400
Put me down!

262
00:16:41,401 --> 00:16:42,960
Lu Feng, where are you two going?

263
00:16:43,520 --> 00:16:44,520
Lu Feng!

264
00:16:45,160 --> 00:16:46,520
Can you just settle down?

265
00:16:46,720 --> 00:16:47,896
You're going to crash into something!

266
00:16:47,920 --> 00:16:48,920
Lu Feng!

267
00:16:53,960 --> 00:16:54,960
You...

268
00:16:58,440 --> 00:17:00,040
I'm going to get some medicine.

269
00:17:09,880 --> 00:17:11,000
I'll be careful.

270
00:18:00,840 --> 00:18:02,000
I just twisted my ankle,

271
00:18:02,160 --> 00:18:03,360
not my hands.

272
00:18:03,760 --> 00:18:05,136
Why do you have to keep feeding me?

273
00:18:05,160 --> 00:18:06,960
You're not happy that
I'm taking care of you?

274
00:18:07,200 --> 00:18:08,200
Open up.

275
00:18:27,200 --> 00:18:28,800
Look at the mess you're making.

276
00:18:38,480 --> 00:18:39,480
Lu Feng?

277
00:18:43,800 --> 00:18:44,800
What's up?

278
00:18:52,800 --> 00:18:54,160
I don't even have to guess.

279
00:18:54,440 --> 00:18:56,040
It's definitely another love letter.

280
00:18:56,360 --> 00:18:57,360
Sometimes I really don't understand

281
00:18:57,361 --> 00:18:58,880
what these girls are thinking.

282
00:18:59,440 --> 00:19:01,176
They ignore a high
quality guy like me,

283
00:19:01,200 --> 00:19:02,200
and instead,

284
00:19:02,520 --> 00:19:04,040
they fall for a playboy like you.

285
00:19:04,520 --> 00:19:05,520
I just don't get it.

286
00:19:06,200 --> 00:19:06,840
What?

287
00:19:07,160 --> 00:19:08,160
Are you jealous?

288
00:19:08,880 --> 00:19:10,760
Have you never received a love letter?

289
00:19:12,320 --> 00:19:14,160
I'm with you all day long,

290
00:19:14,440 --> 00:19:16,840
you completely overshadow me.

291
00:19:17,080 --> 00:19:18,480
How could anyone possibly like me?

292
00:19:18,920 --> 00:19:19,920
No way.

293
00:19:20,440 --> 00:19:21,440
From now on,

294
00:19:22,480 --> 00:19:23,680
I need to stay away from you.

295
00:19:26,680 --> 00:19:27,680
You wouldn't dare.

296
00:19:28,640 --> 00:19:30,120
I wouldn't, I wouldn't. Happy now?

297
00:19:36,360 --> 00:19:37,360
Xiao Chen,

298
00:19:37,440 --> 00:19:38,440
are you...

299
00:19:39,680 --> 00:19:40,856
thinking about dating someone?

300
00:19:40,880 --> 00:19:41,880
Of course.

301
00:19:46,520 --> 00:19:47,920
I guess so.

302
00:19:50,120 --> 00:19:51,840
I need you to promise me one thing.

303
00:19:53,760 --> 00:19:55,200
As long as I don't date any girls,

304
00:19:57,800 --> 00:19:58,800
can you...

305
00:19:58,960 --> 00:20:00,440
not like any girls either?

306
00:20:00,760 --> 00:20:02,120
What kind of request is that?

307
00:20:04,480 --> 00:20:05,120
Don't ask.

308
00:20:05,360 --> 00:20:06,480
Just promise me.

309
00:20:08,240 --> 00:20:09,680
Fine, fine, fine.

310
00:20:09,800 --> 00:20:10,920
I promise, okay?

311
00:20:46,520 --> 00:20:47,520
Xiao Chen,

312
00:20:53,320 --> 00:20:54,680
will you miss me during the break?

313
00:20:55,160 --> 00:20:56,400
Who would miss you?

314
00:20:57,280 --> 00:20:59,480
Say it again. Will you miss me?

315
00:21:00,160 --> 00:21:01,696
Alright, alright. I'll
miss you, I'll miss you.

316
00:21:01,720 --> 00:21:02,400
Let go!

317
00:21:02,560 --> 00:21:03,720
You're hurting my neck.

318
00:21:04,160 --> 00:21:05,320
That's better.

319
00:21:07,080 --> 00:21:08,080
Lu Feng.

320
00:21:23,960 --> 00:21:24,960
Brother,

321
00:21:26,480 --> 00:21:27,920
want to hear the new song I learned?

322
00:22:22,720 --> 00:22:24,240
Hello, who are you looking for?

323
00:22:24,480 --> 00:22:25,480
Xiao Chen!

324
00:22:26,800 --> 00:22:27,800
Lu Feng?

325
00:22:27,960 --> 00:22:29,136
Did something happen at your place?

326
00:22:29,160 --> 00:22:30,240
Why are you crying so hard?

327
00:22:31,720 --> 00:22:32,856
Something happened at your place!

328
00:22:32,880 --> 00:22:34,080
My mom is just watching TV.

329
00:22:38,040 --> 00:22:39,040
Classmate,

330
00:22:43,080 --> 00:22:44,840
Xiao Chen, Happy New Year!

331
00:22:45,040 --> 00:22:45,720
Am I the first one

332
00:22:45,721 --> 00:22:46,881
to wish you a Happy New Year?

333
00:22:46,920 --> 00:22:48,376
New Year's isn't until
the day after tomorrow.

334
00:22:48,400 --> 00:22:50,160
It doesn't count if you say it today.

335
00:22:51,320 --> 00:22:52,520
If I say it counts, it counts.

336
00:22:52,840 --> 00:22:54,000
Xiao Chen, did you miss me?

337
00:22:54,120 --> 00:22:56,480
Can you stop saying things like that?

338
00:22:57,800 --> 00:22:59,280
Just tell me, did you or didn't you?

339
00:23:01,800 --> 00:23:03,000
A little bit, I guess.

340
00:23:04,680 --> 00:23:06,440
I missed you way more than a little bit.

341
00:23:06,840 --> 00:23:07,840
Missed me my foot.

342
00:23:07,880 --> 00:23:09,680
You seem to be having
a great time out there.

343
00:23:25,360 --> 00:23:26,480
Anyway, I'm hanging up now.

344
00:23:28,400 --> 00:23:29,400
Xiao Chen,

345
00:23:29,480 --> 00:23:31,200
who were you on the phone with for so long?

346
00:23:31,320 --> 00:23:32,320
A classmate.

347
00:23:33,960 --> 00:23:34,680
A girl?

348
00:23:34,920 --> 00:23:35,960
A boy.

349
00:23:38,280 --> 00:23:39,280
Xiao Chen,

350
00:23:39,640 --> 00:23:40,960
you're only a freshman.

351
00:23:41,360 --> 00:23:42,760
You should focus on your studies.

352
00:23:43,240 --> 00:23:45,160
Think about dating after you graduate.

353
00:23:45,480 --> 00:23:46,480
Who's dating?

354
00:23:46,640 --> 00:23:47,400
Why don't you call back

355
00:23:47,520 --> 00:23:48,520
and see if it's a guy?

356
00:23:48,800 --> 00:23:49,800
It really is a guy...!

357
00:23:50,000 --> 00:23:51,080
Really.

358
00:23:51,840 --> 00:23:52,880
Mom, just eat your dinner.

359
00:23:53,080 --> 00:23:54,840
Otherwise, Chen-chen
is going to eat it all.

360
00:23:56,760 --> 00:23:57,480
Eat up.

361
00:23:57,720 --> 00:23:59,320
If the kid says it's not, then it's not.

362
00:23:59,760 --> 00:24:00,280
Eat.

363
00:24:00,480 --> 00:24:02,320
Here, have some greens.

364
00:24:03,120 --> 00:24:04,120
Here, Chen-chen.

365
00:24:11,560 --> 00:24:12,200
Xiao Chen,

366
00:24:12,360 --> 00:24:13,360
Lu Feng,

367
00:24:39,800 --> 00:24:40,960
I forgot to buy oil again.

368
00:24:41,600 --> 00:24:43,879
If you're lucky, you can taste it later.

369
00:24:43,880 --> 00:24:44,360
Old Cheng,

370
00:24:44,360 --> 00:24:45,360
I'll talk to you later.

371
00:24:45,440 --> 00:24:46,440
Old Cheng,

372
00:24:48,320 --> 00:24:49,640
I forgot to buy oil yesterday.

373
00:24:49,880 --> 00:24:51,200
There's not a drop left.

374
00:24:51,400 --> 00:24:52,400
Go buy another bottle.

375
00:24:52,880 --> 00:24:53,880
Okay, okay.

376
00:24:53,960 --> 00:24:55,320
I'll put on a jacket and go.

377
00:24:57,353 --> 00:24:58,393
Xiao Chen,

378
00:24:58,480 --> 00:25:00,840
don't talk on the phone with
your classmates for so long.

379
00:25:00,920 --> 00:25:02,080
Phone bills are expensive.

380
00:25:02,760 --> 00:25:03,320
Mom,

381
00:25:03,440 --> 00:25:05,480
you don't need to worry
about the world's problems.

382
00:25:05,600 --> 00:25:07,640
He called me, I didn't call him.

383
00:25:08,040 --> 00:25:10,080
His family isn't short on cash.

384
00:25:10,640 --> 00:25:12,279
Whatever you have to say, say it at school.

385
00:25:12,280 --> 00:25:13,520
It's the same thing.

386
00:25:13,920 --> 00:25:15,896
Long-distance calls within the
province are 60 cents a minute.

387
00:25:15,920 --> 00:25:17,160
An hour is 36 yuan.

388
00:25:17,400 --> 00:25:18,320
Two hours is 72 yuan.

389
00:25:18,321 --> 00:25:19,801
That's enough to buy a bottle of oil!

390
00:25:21,560 --> 00:25:23,480
It's rare for Mom to be so good at math,

391
00:25:23,840 --> 00:25:24,840
and so sharp-minded.

392
00:25:25,600 --> 00:25:26,600
You young people

393
00:25:26,640 --> 00:25:27,920
just don't know how hard it is

394
00:25:28,000 --> 00:25:29,280
for parents to earn money.

395
00:25:35,160 --> 00:25:36,360
My mom's gone.

396
00:25:37,440 --> 00:25:38,440
Lu Feng,

397
00:25:38,840 --> 00:25:40,920
maybe we should stop calling each other.

398
00:25:41,400 --> 00:25:42,400
If you do the math,

399
00:25:42,560 --> 00:25:44,000
you've spent quite a bit of money.

400
00:25:44,280 --> 00:25:45,720
Fine, I won't call then.

401
00:25:46,040 --> 00:25:47,040
You...

402
00:25:47,073 --> 00:25:48,553
you're just going to agree like that?

403
00:25:49,240 --> 00:25:50,560
I've always been decisive.

404
00:25:52,360 --> 00:25:53,480
I'll call you then.

405
00:25:54,400 --> 00:25:55,880
Like phone calls are free for you?

406
00:25:56,360 --> 00:25:58,120
No, we don't need to call.

407
00:25:58,200 --> 00:25:59,200
You...

408
00:26:01,760 --> 00:26:02,920
Xiao Chen, go open the door.

409
00:26:03,040 --> 00:26:04,320
It might be the milk delivery.

410
00:26:06,720 --> 00:26:07,720
Uncle,

411
00:26:08,240 --> 00:26:09,240
It's the New Year,

412
00:26:09,600 --> 00:26:10,840
and you're still

413
00:26:12,800 --> 00:26:13,800
working?

414
00:26:14,160 --> 00:26:15,160
Uncle?

415
00:26:17,906 --> 00:26:18,586
Hello, sir.

416
00:26:18,920 --> 00:26:19,200
Hello.

417
00:26:19,200 --> 00:26:20,200
Hello, ma'am.

418
00:26:20,440 --> 00:26:21,080
My name is Lu Feng.

419
00:26:21,200 --> 00:26:22,280
I'm Xiao Chen's classmate.

420
00:26:22,520 --> 00:26:23,856
I came to wish you a happy New Year.

421
00:26:23,880 --> 00:26:24,880
Come on in!

422
00:26:24,960 --> 00:26:25,960
Happy New Year.

423
00:26:26,120 --> 00:26:28,280
You're just a kid, why bring gifts?

424
00:26:28,560 --> 00:26:29,600
It's the least I could do.

425
00:26:29,880 --> 00:26:30,880
Olive oil?

426
00:26:30,920 --> 00:26:32,160
We just ran out!

427
00:26:32,920 --> 00:26:33,920
Xiao Chen,

428
00:26:34,240 --> 00:26:36,440
You didn't even tell me
your classmate was coming.

429
00:26:36,600 --> 00:26:37,896
Exactly. Why are you just standing there?

430
00:26:37,920 --> 00:26:39,480
Go on, make your friend comfortable.

431
00:26:42,353 --> 00:26:44,273
Old Cheng, go buy some more good food.

432
00:26:44,520 --> 00:26:45,200
Sure, sure.

433
00:26:45,280 --> 00:26:46,480
No need to buy oil, okay?

434
00:26:46,560 --> 00:26:48,016
Sir, you don't need to buy that much.

435
00:26:48,040 --> 00:26:49,040
Alright.

436
00:26:49,200 --> 00:26:49,680
Go on.

437
00:26:49,880 --> 00:26:51,240
Peel some oranges for your friend.

438
00:26:51,600 --> 00:26:52,600
Sit down, sit down.

439
00:26:57,958 --> 00:27:00,798
[Messages from Lu Feng's dad
threatening him to come home immediately]

440
00:27:02,680 --> 00:27:05,240
Why are you here at
my house so suddenly?

441
00:27:05,680 --> 00:27:07,960
Because I missed you, obviously.

442
00:27:08,040 --> 00:27:09,160
Keep your hands to yourself.

443
00:27:09,560 --> 00:27:10,680
How did you find my address?

444
00:27:10,960 --> 00:27:12,760
It's all in the school records.

445
00:27:13,920 --> 00:27:15,056
You're so good with your hands.

446
00:27:15,080 --> 00:27:16,880
I love apples cut like this.

447
00:27:19,160 --> 00:27:20,320
Wasn't that for me?

448
00:27:33,640 --> 00:27:34,640
Who is this?

449
00:27:34,880 --> 00:27:35,880
My brother.

450
00:27:36,000 --> 00:27:37,000
You have a brother?

451
00:27:38,640 --> 00:27:39,800
How old were you here?

452
00:27:42,347 --> 00:27:43,387
I don't even remember.

453
00:27:44,120 --> 00:27:45,640
You don't even know your own age?

454
00:27:46,680 --> 00:27:48,600
Did you like sunflowers
since you were little?

455
00:27:51,000 --> 00:27:52,000
So cute.

456
00:27:55,640 --> 00:27:57,840
Why were your eyes so
big in your baby photo?

457
00:28:06,720 --> 00:28:07,720
Give it here.

458
00:28:09,680 --> 00:28:10,680
Give it to me.

459
00:28:12,640 --> 00:28:13,640
My brother and I

460
00:28:13,840 --> 00:28:15,880
were always called
handsome by the neighbors.

461
00:28:17,120 --> 00:28:18,520
The one who just breezed through,

462
00:28:19,240 --> 00:28:20,240
that's your brother?

463
00:28:23,760 --> 00:28:24,960
You're still the handsome one.

464
00:28:25,240 --> 00:28:25,840
Let me show you.

465
00:28:25,841 --> 00:28:27,400
My favorite childhood toys.

466
00:28:32,520 --> 00:28:33,160
These cards.

467
00:28:33,161 --> 00:28:34,600
I spent so long collecting these.

468
00:28:34,760 --> 00:28:35,520
They're all limited editions.

469
00:28:35,640 --> 00:28:37,280
You can't find these just anywhere.

470
00:28:38,040 --> 00:28:38,560
And this,

471
00:28:38,680 --> 00:28:39,520
the game console.

472
00:28:39,600 --> 00:28:41,000
I was a beast at all the games.

473
00:28:42,760 --> 00:28:43,240
And this,

474
00:28:43,400 --> 00:28:44,400
the airplane game.

475
00:28:44,520 --> 00:28:46,560
I was absolutely invincible at it.

476
00:29:00,400 --> 00:29:01,640
Don't be shy, eat up.

477
00:29:02,000 --> 00:29:03,400
Thank you, sir. And this seafood...

478
00:29:03,840 --> 00:29:05,120
- Thank you, ma'am.
- It's so fresh.

479
00:29:06,040 --> 00:29:06,840
Lu Feng,

480
00:29:07,033 --> 00:29:08,393
since you're here, stay the night.

481
00:29:08,480 --> 00:29:09,520
Stay for a few days.

482
00:29:09,800 --> 00:29:11,560
Just bunk with Xiao Chen.

483
00:29:11,720 --> 00:29:12,720
Yes, exactly.

484
00:29:12,760 --> 00:29:14,640
Xiao Chen can be your guide tomorrow

485
00:29:14,760 --> 00:29:15,520
and show you around.

486
00:29:15,521 --> 00:29:17,121
Wait, why is he staying with my brother?

487
00:29:18,360 --> 00:29:19,776
Well, do you want him
to stay with you instead?

488
00:29:19,800 --> 00:29:21,680
Don't be rude. Just eat.

489
00:29:23,440 --> 00:29:23,840
Eat.

490
00:29:23,841 --> 00:29:25,880
Ma'am, I have to leave tomorrow.

491
00:29:27,240 --> 00:29:28,280
So soon?

492
00:29:29,480 --> 00:29:30,600
My dad wants me home.

493
00:29:31,160 --> 00:29:32,480
You two are very close, then?

494
00:29:36,240 --> 00:29:37,240
Eat, eat, here.

495
00:29:37,280 --> 00:29:38,560
Eat more. You guys eat more too.

496
00:29:39,280 --> 00:29:39,880
Ma'am,

497
00:29:40,120 --> 00:29:40,600
thank you.

498
00:29:40,680 --> 00:29:42,000
Go on, eat it while it's hot.

499
00:29:47,240 --> 00:29:48,240
Here.

500
00:29:48,480 --> 00:29:49,280
Come on, it's New Year's.

501
00:29:49,480 --> 00:29:50,560
Welcome to our home.

502
00:29:50,640 --> 00:29:51,640
Thank you for having me.

503
00:29:51,800 --> 00:29:52,440
Happy New Year.

504
00:29:52,520 --> 00:29:53,760
Happy New Year, happy New Year.

505
00:29:53,880 --> 00:29:54,640
Happy New Year.

506
00:29:54,760 --> 00:29:55,280
Happy.

507
00:29:55,600 --> 00:29:56,600
You brat.

508
00:30:44,280 --> 00:30:45,280
Lu Feng,

509
00:30:46,000 --> 00:30:47,200
are you cold?

510
00:30:48,720 --> 00:30:49,720
Yeah.

511
00:30:50,640 --> 00:30:51,720
It's actually pretty cold.

512
00:30:54,240 --> 00:30:55,240
You...

513
00:30:58,760 --> 00:31:00,040
Do you want to...

514
00:31:09,600 --> 00:31:11,000
I... I mean,

515
00:31:11,360 --> 00:31:13,600
you take the bed, I'll sleep on the floor.

516
00:31:16,040 --> 00:31:17,200
Won't you be cold then?

517
00:31:17,920 --> 00:31:18,920
But...

518
00:31:20,200 --> 00:31:22,160
my bed is too small.

519
00:31:30,760 --> 00:31:31,760
How about this?

520
00:31:32,640 --> 00:31:33,640
Isn't this better?

521
00:32:06,720 --> 00:32:08,160
Still cold?

522
00:32:20,820 --> 00:32:21,900
Not anymore.

523
00:32:58,400 --> 00:32:59,400
Lu Feng,

524
00:32:59,440 --> 00:33:01,120
- I brought you some pork floss my mom made.
- I got some chocolate for you.

525
00:33:17,160 --> 00:33:18,440
I haven't had the nerve to ask,

526
00:33:19,000 --> 00:33:20,240
but what happened to your face?

527
00:33:21,960 --> 00:33:22,960
Where did you run off to?

528
00:33:23,360 --> 00:33:24,520
Get back here right now!

529
00:33:24,760 --> 00:33:26,120
Don't think I can't handle you.

530
00:33:28,960 --> 00:33:30,880
My dad hit me. Believe it or not.

531
00:33:32,360 --> 00:33:34,160
You're this old and
your dad still hits you?

532
00:33:35,440 --> 00:33:36,600
My dad is terrifying.

533
00:33:37,040 --> 00:33:39,480
If I don't listen to him, he beats me.

534
00:33:42,040 --> 00:33:43,080
There's only one left.

535
00:33:43,560 --> 00:33:44,760
Why didn't you save it for me?

536
00:34:04,960 --> 00:34:05,960
You jerk.

537
00:34:06,800 --> 00:34:07,840
Are you crazy?

538
00:34:46,480 --> 00:34:47,880
I'm not like Lu Feng.

539
00:34:49,160 --> 00:34:50,880
He's used to joking around,

540
00:34:52,440 --> 00:34:53,960
and he doesn't know when to stop.

541
00:34:56,080 --> 00:34:57,280
But whatever I do,

542
00:34:58,080 --> 00:34:59,320
I want to do it properly.

543
00:35:13,440 --> 00:35:14,880
So many girls have confessed to you,

544
00:35:14,920 --> 00:35:16,480
and you don't like any of them?

545
00:35:17,560 --> 00:35:18,560
No problem.

546
00:35:21,600 --> 00:35:23,280
None of them are as cute as Xiao Chen.

547
00:35:23,800 --> 00:35:25,320
None of them are as good as Xiao Chen.

548
00:35:26,080 --> 00:35:27,359
None of them treat me as well as Xiao Chen.

549
00:35:27,360 --> 00:35:30,400
Then you should just marry Xiao Chen.

550
00:35:30,560 --> 00:35:31,560
Yeah, exactly!

551
00:35:33,080 --> 00:35:34,080
Lu Feng,

552
00:35:34,520 --> 00:35:35,520
go Lu Feng!

553
00:35:37,360 --> 00:35:38,360
What are you doing?

554
00:35:43,560 --> 00:35:45,040
Stop acting crazy, I'm getting angry.

555
00:35:49,760 --> 00:35:51,416
If you want to mess around,
go find someone else.

556
00:35:51,440 --> 00:35:52,680
Don't use me as your scapegoat.

557
00:35:54,600 --> 00:35:55,600
Are you mad?

558
00:35:56,640 --> 00:35:59,160
I can't understand his bizarre behavior.

559
00:35:59,640 --> 00:36:03,160
And I can't stand his
frivolous, grinning attitude.

560
00:36:08,360 --> 00:36:10,160
You're Lu Feng's friend,
Cheng Yichen, right?

561
00:36:10,720 --> 00:36:12,120
I... yes, I am.

562
00:36:12,320 --> 00:36:13,360
I'm his sister, Lu Yu.

563
00:36:13,800 --> 00:36:15,359
He got into a fight at a bar last night

564
00:36:15,360 --> 00:36:16,360
and got stabbed.

565
00:36:16,480 --> 00:36:18,360
He's in room 307 at the City Hospital.

566
00:36:18,560 --> 00:36:20,056
I really don't have time
to deal with him right now.

567
00:36:20,080 --> 00:36:21,120
Could you go check on him?

568
00:36:31,640 --> 00:36:33,520
You shouldn't be running
around the hospital.

569
00:36:44,960 --> 00:36:45,960
Lu Feng,

570
00:36:46,160 --> 00:36:47,160
are you okay?

571
00:36:47,480 --> 00:36:48,480
Xiao Chen,

572
00:36:48,520 --> 00:36:49,320
why are you here?

573
00:36:49,440 --> 00:36:50,360
Looks like you're fine.

574
00:36:50,440 --> 00:36:51,440
I'm leaving.

575
00:36:59,360 --> 00:37:00,440
Why is it still bleeding?

576
00:37:01,000 --> 00:37:02,640
Should we find a doctor to re-bandage it?

577
00:37:04,200 --> 00:37:06,520
You're worried about me, so
you're not mad anymore, right?

578
00:37:10,120 --> 00:37:12,120
You haven't spoken to me for six days.

579
00:37:13,080 --> 00:37:15,920
Why does he remember how
many days has it been so clearly?

580
00:37:17,000 --> 00:37:18,280
Let's just go find a doctor.

581
00:37:20,040 --> 00:37:21,040
This blood...

582
00:37:21,320 --> 00:37:23,400
it's just from when it
was bandaged yesterday.

583
00:37:23,880 --> 00:37:24,960
It's fine now.

584
00:37:26,840 --> 00:37:28,560
How did you know I was here?

585
00:37:30,520 --> 00:37:31,720
Your sister said you were hurt

586
00:37:32,640 --> 00:37:33,680
and called me

587
00:37:34,080 --> 00:37:35,240
to come take care of you.

588
00:37:36,920 --> 00:37:39,040
She's such a tiger.

589
00:37:39,560 --> 00:37:40,760
I told her on the phone

590
00:37:40,880 --> 00:37:42,400
it was just a scratch.

591
00:37:43,680 --> 00:37:46,360
Actually, I was just asking her for money.

592
00:37:46,760 --> 00:37:48,920
The bar is trying to charge me for damages.

593
00:37:50,160 --> 00:37:51,160
Lu Feng,

594
00:37:51,520 --> 00:37:53,000
if you're really okay,

595
00:37:53,360 --> 00:37:54,360
I'm going to head out.

596
00:37:57,360 --> 00:37:58,360
What are you doing?

597
00:38:00,440 --> 00:38:01,800
I think this injury

598
00:38:02,360 --> 00:38:03,480
was worth it.

599
00:38:04,040 --> 00:38:04,800
Are you sick?

600
00:38:04,960 --> 00:38:06,360
How is getting hurt worth anything?

601
00:38:12,080 --> 00:38:13,200
If I hadn't gotten hurt,

602
00:38:14,600 --> 00:38:15,920
you wouldn't have come to see me.

603
00:38:17,400 --> 00:38:18,160
Don't worry.

604
00:38:18,400 --> 00:38:19,600
If you ever kick the bucket,

605
00:38:19,720 --> 00:38:21,200
I'll be sure to come pay my respects.

606
00:38:23,640 --> 00:38:25,520
How come you're not
wearing your glasses today?

607
00:38:27,440 --> 00:38:28,680
I have no idea where they went.
